description: Crepes Bonaparte recreates the experience of enjoying French crepes on the streets of Paris, France with their made to order breakfast, lunch, and dessert style crepes. Crepes Bonaparte has been featured on Food Network’s ‘The Great Food Truck Race’ and Cooking Channel’s ‘Food Truck Revolution’ and ‘Eat Street.’ Crepes Bonaparte was named by QSR Magazine as one of the Top 20 Food Trucks in America.
name: Crepes Bonaparte
